<header class="masthead">
  <div class="container h-100">
    <div class="row h-100">
      <div class="col-lg-10 align-self-end">
        <h1 class="text-white font-weight-bold">Your Favorite Source of Free Bootstrap Themes</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <p class="text-white font-weight-light mb-5">Start Bootstrap can help you build better websites using the Bootstrap framework! Just download a theme and start customizing, no strings attached!</p>
